Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.34,0:00:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要走了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:17.41,0:00:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位保重了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:20.65,0:00:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過去對您的諸多無禮\N還請見諒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.81,0:00:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.60,0:01:12.03,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,just keep on trying, keep on flying\N{\c&HFFBF00&}just keep on trying, keep on flying
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:12.10,0:01:15.66,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be the light\N{\c&HFFBF00&}I will be the light
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:15.74,0:01:22.87,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說把黎明　當作是一個開始\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜明けをひと　つの始まりとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.94,0:01:29.91,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說現在就是來臨的時刻\N{\c&HFFBF00&}今が来るべき時だとするなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.98,0:01:36.15,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,與你的煙雲時代交響曲 飛向雲海的彼端 \N{\c&HFFBF00&}君とのCloud Age Symphony  雲の海の向こうに
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.22,0:01:43.86,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,飛往光芒照射的方向\N{\c&HFFBF00&}光が射す方へ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.53,0:01:58.81,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah～是否可以遇見有如魔法的那瞬間？\N{\c&HFFBF00&}Ah～魔法のような一瞬に会えるのか？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.88,0:02:13.32,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,取代寒冷的黑夜  我倆展翅飛翔\N{\c&HFFBF00&}冷たい夜を引き替えに  二人は羽ばたいて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:13.39,0:02:23.74,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,在那盡頭  抓住了永恆…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}永远を掴む、その果てには
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.75,0:02:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H8dccf0&}突破作戰\NBreakthrough
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:48.86,0:02:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一手不需要考慮這麼久吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.50,0:02:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,英麥曼你的心…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.01,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知為何顯得很亂哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.78,0:03:12.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,簡單的說，副艦長她身分尊貴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.89,0:03:14.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等她回到官廷裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.69,0:03:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是就會變成我們的敵人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們以後到底會怎樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.73,0:03:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八成死路一條吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少蠢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.77,0:03:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想也知道副艦長她不是那種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.43,0:03:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不快埋頭幹活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.20,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.14,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了，莫藍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.47,0:03:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹嘛一副要死不活的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.24,0:03:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難不成你還想\N高攀人家副艦長嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.95,0:03:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位…請問你們\N都是為了什麼而登上這艘船呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是為了出人頭地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.16,0:03:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了過更好的生活\N才來當船員的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.50,0:04:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無聊話少說，快幹活吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.77,0:04:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:10.44,0:04:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我可是個槍兵耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.28,0:04:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可以在這裡掃地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.42,0:04:17.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哦，男兒當自強哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.16,0:04:28.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這次換了小帥哥上場啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.56,0:04:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請問…蘇菲亞在哪裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.64,0:04:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下剛才已經離艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.94,0:04:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說殿下是指…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:40.27,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦，你不知道啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.04,0:04:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,副艦長她是皇帝的女兒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.61,0:04:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.55,0:04:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來是不可能\N不過這的確是真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.35,0:04:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說她上船原本是為了\N負責監視艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.52,0:04:56.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,結果卻對艦長一見鍾情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.59,0:04:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,活生生一部官廷羅曼史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.56,0:05:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長他好歹也來送人家一下嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,憑他的個性甭想啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.30,0:05:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下又是怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.20,0:05:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能說他正值青春期囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.71,0:05:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天到底是怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.02,0:05:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，終於找到你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.78,0:05:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你到哪兒去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:26.89,0:05:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,待…待會兒再說吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.89,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士你好怪哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.37,0:05:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.68,0:05:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要回帝都去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.69,0:06:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來你是不會挽留我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有挽留妳的理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.16,0:06:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的打算除掉戴芬妮總帥嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.87,0:06:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就是為了這個才活著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.55,0:06:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉絲她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.72,0:06:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已經不在了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.13,0:06:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.57,0:06:48.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼不阻止蘇菲亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.87,0:06:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞她很想和你在一起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.77,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你真的什麼都沒搞懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.80,0:07:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麥德賽艦隊\N已經和度西斯碰上了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這下就可以把度西斯的殘黨…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.37,0:07:24.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,萬萬不可
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.11,0:07:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失去了祖國的度西斯艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.98,0:07:29.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好比是一頭受傷的獅子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.01,0:07:31.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對他們出手是很危險的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.11,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害怕了嗎，馬留司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.11,0:07:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在正是消滅度西斯\N千載難逢的大好機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.32,0:07:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，請您以您的慈悲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.95,0:07:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,賜予度西斯人民一塊居留地\N才是上上之策
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.90,0:07:51.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朕剛才已經把\N度西斯派來的使者給斬首了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.57,0:07:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼回事，馬留司
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.60,0:07:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要阻止也來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.64,0:07:58.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,退下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.57,0:08:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朕命你閉門思過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.39,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳變了不少呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.39,0:08:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我搞不好比較喜歡現在的妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.00,0:08:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,裝彈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.44,0:08:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真有精神
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.57,0:08:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.58,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.51,0:08:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是莫藍啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.28,0:08:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是槍兵嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.38,0:08:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在很多戰艦上都打過仗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.59,0:08:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,布留納克號，艾斯塔號\N克勞索拉斯號
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.29,0:08:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來你還是位歷經沙場的勇士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.90,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你知道槍兵的生存率是多少嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.34,0:09:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有區區的三成耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.24,0:09:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,意思是說只要上了三次戰場\N絕大部份都難以倖存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.31,0:09:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而幾次走過死亡邊緣\N最後換來的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.41,0:09:12.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不過就是…這個而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.25,0:09:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要和我…一起下船呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.42,0:09:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼是找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.12,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,…所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.53,0:09:32.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來我是還沒開始\N就已經出局了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.20,0:09:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起，請妳忘了我說的話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.62,0:09:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是來解決上次那件事情嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.69,0:09:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瞧瞧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.83,0:10:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是下到這一步吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.73,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚\N蘇菲亞她到我房間來找我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.00,0:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兵升變
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.64,0:10:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一來兵就成了皇后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.18,0:10:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想該是進攻基爾特的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:20.21,0:10:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是強硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.65,0:10:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要解決掉敵方的國王\N一切就可以結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.82,0:10:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，該說是皇后吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.52,0:10:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,若你還有時間去管黑子的皇后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:31.73,0:10:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我勸你還是應該先守好\N你身邊的白子皇后才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.71,0:10:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,塔琪安娜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.65,0:10:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.82,0:10:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.05,0:11:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.76,0:11:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你快帶著拉薇下船去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.69,0:11:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長他打算要\N直衝基爾特公會的本部
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.63,0:11:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那塔琪安娜妳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.40,0:11:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我能待的地方也只有這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.68,0:11:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,各位，我們已經失去了故鄉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.95,0:11:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們唯一的選擇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.98,0:11:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是在這片土地上\N建立一個新的度西斯國
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:34.42,0:11:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們要向安那托勒\N下最後的決戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.69,0:11:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了死去的同胞們\N我們必須要活下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.43,0:11:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再次重建我們的光榮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.76,0:11:45.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為度西斯而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.07,0:11:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為度西斯而戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.15,0:12:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜大人就任烏爾班號艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.49,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這船坐起來挺舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.26,0:12:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.16,0:12:19.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有一架身分不明的大型貨櫃\N進到了我方的防空領域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.50,0:12:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快把它給我打下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.13,0:12:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是不發出停船警告\N就直接開砲恐怕不妥吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是慶祝我新官上任不行啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.51,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別囉嗦快打就是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.51,0:12:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.44,0:12:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備砲擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:35.85,0:12:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面有皇帝的徽章
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.95,0:12:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那…那不是\N蘇菲亞殿下的御用專機嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,停止砲擊，快停止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.14,0:12:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下駕到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:01.01,0:13:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤莉絲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下您看來身體依然健朗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.12,0:13:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您要怎麼解釋\N您協助銀之戰艦叛亂一事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.73,0:13:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那並不是叛亂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.19,0:13:24.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是陛下有四艘戰艦遭到擊沈\N又該怎麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.40,0:13:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為對方主動攻擊\N才不得不應戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.54,0:13:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是強辯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不許無禮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.40,0:13:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下，度西斯已毀於嚴寒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.27,0:13:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我安那托勒也正受到酷熱侵襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.01,0:13:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是打仗的時候了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.51,0:13:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,務請陛下重新考慮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.92,0:13:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的意思我都聽明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.02,0:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有這份愛民之心與溫柔善良
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.16,0:13:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為父的感覺十分高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.50,0:13:57.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.93,0:14:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，妳想要給大家的這瓶水\N卻偏偏只有一份
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.90,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把這瓶水留給本國的人民\N是身為一國之君的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.24,0:14:13.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞，妳的行為不端\N將陷為父的於不義
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.61,0:14:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,陛下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.71,0:14:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把蘇菲亞送到塔上關起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.18,0:14:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下啊，父王
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.97,0:14:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘇菲亞殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.98,0:14:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.15,0:14:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是馬留司嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.45,0:14:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您沒有受傷吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.85,0:14:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有，但是我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.59,0:14:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒能做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.32,0:14:55.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您原諒我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:56.06,0:14:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不該讓您一個人\N背負這麼大的重任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.39,0:15:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是\N這樣我回來就沒有意義了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.93,0:15:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論在何處\N我總是什麼忙都幫不上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自從女兒死後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.11,0:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直就把妳視如己出\N來撫養長大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.08,0:15:23.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這一切也只到今天了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬留司…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:26.15,0:15:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您答應我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.99,0:15:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,您一定要登上王位\N好接下我未完成的工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.09,0:15:34.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.53,0:15:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在一切結束之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.26,0:15:38.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就請蘇菲亞殿下您先待在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.04,0:15:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.74,0:15:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請您不要把愛只獻給一個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.94,0:15:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而要獻給全民百姓才是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:54.71,0:15:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,馬留司…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.76,0:16:07.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你有話就快說啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.26,0:16:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我認為\N拉薇妳離開這艘船會比較好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.47,0:16:13.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.23,0:16:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為這裡太危險了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.47,0:16:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亞力克斯他似乎打算\N要進攻基爾特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.07,0:16:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此我們就一起離開嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.14,0:16:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想弄清楚\N這片天空到底發生了什麼事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.38,0:16:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我也要留下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然要攻打基爾特那正好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.52,0:16:36.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就用爸爸他們的先鋒艇\N來飛越大風暴區吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.09,0:16:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…並不是爸爸他們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:44.26,0:16:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這架先鋒艇\N當初是亞力克斯駕駛的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.84,0:16:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直瞞著妳，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.68,0:17:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以餘生來說\N這也算是活得夠久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.37,0:17:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.34,0:17:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是度西斯的殘存艦隊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左舷推進力下降
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.87,0:17:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射擊指揮室連絡中斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵，全速脫離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:31.24,0:17:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓烏爾班號\N被擊沈在這種地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.21,0:17:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.75,0:17:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左滿舵，全速脫離中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.40,0:17:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然膽敢用夜襲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.17,0:17:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,烏爾班號到底在做什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.20,0:17:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,準備射擊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.14,0:18:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:05.81,0:18:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會發生這種事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.22,0:18:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來度西斯的主力軍\N趁著黑夜全集合到帝都來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.89,0:18:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個不用你說也看得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:17.16,0:18:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,潘朵拉巨砲呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去帝都會被攻陷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.13,0:18:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請陛下禪位給蘇菲亞殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,立刻退位吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:28.37,0:18:30.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當初朕拔擢了\N被基爾特趕出來的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.60,0:18:32.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給了你今天的地位
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.51,0:18:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而你居然要恩將仇報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.01,0:19:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,整個城市…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.66,0:19:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是父王的命令嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.73,0:19:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,六號準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.63,0:19:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,七號準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.90,0:19:35.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,八號準備就緒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.90,0:19:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,距離呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.80,0:19:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已進入射程範圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:39.77,0:19:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好，發射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.97,0:19:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等皇官遭到佔領後\N再來攻擊就太遲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:52.35,0:19:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打到了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.62,0:19:54.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,命中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.69,0:19:56.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一發，快點
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:59.06,0:20:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.16,0:20:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呆瓜，命令已經失效了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.14,0:20:10.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,文生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.87,0:20:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請原諒我，蘇菲亞殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.81,0:20:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.38,0:20:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上次見到您是在官校裡吧\N公主殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.41,0:20:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼會在這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:21.18,0:20:23.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是個靠得住的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:25.72,0:20:26.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已準備好一艘\N比銀之戰艦更高檔的戰艦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:29.76,0:20:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來，我給你一個新任務
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.61,0:20:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看著這群螻蟻，還真有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要收回組件嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:52.01,0:20:53.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨他們去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.89,0:21:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,艦長，我一直在等您回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:09.26,0:21:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,前任艦長呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.36,0:21:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,落荒而逃了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.00,0:21:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以重新把烏爾班號交給我嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.04,0:21:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我准許
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:20.81,0:21:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這位是蘇菲亞殿下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.28,0:21:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不久她就是皇帝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.29,0:21:38.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也不曉得該怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:40.83,0:21:41.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.26,0:21:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得這道傷痕嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:44.30,0:21:47.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是當初在練習時\N撞到畜欄所留下的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:47.93,0:21:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個是在比賽時\N刮到牆壁留下來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.27,0:21:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉薇…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:52.71,0:21:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個小傢伙並不屬於其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:56.64,0:21:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它是我們的先鋒艇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.15,0:22:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:01.41,0:22:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論任何時候\N克勞士你總是會筆直看著目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:05.45,0:22:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起飛越大風暴區
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:07.69,0:22:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是我們從小的夢想嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:10.92,0:22:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但你現在卻表現得婆婆媽媽的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:13.83,0:22:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭這樣的克勞士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:36.02,0:22:40.28,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,黑夜的時光逐漸逼近\N{\c&HFFBF00&}夜の時間が迫り来る
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.92,0:22:46.82,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你離我如此接近感覺  卻好遠…\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたはこんな近く でも遠い…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.89,0:22:52.23,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你的憧憬是什麼\N{\c&HFFBF00&}何に憧れて
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.30,0:22:58.10,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,心中想的又是誰\N{\c&HFFBF00&}だれを想うのか
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.17,0:23:03.77,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,你奮不顧身的身影\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いのち賭ける姿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.84,0:23:12.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,有一種透明的美麗  令我噤聲無言\N{\c&HFFBF00&}透き通る美しさに 言葉を飲んだ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:12.62,0:23:18.49,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,如果你欲飛往天際\N{\c&HFFBF00&}あなたが空を行くなら
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:18.56,0:23:24.26,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,我願成為你的翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}わたしは翼になりたい
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:24.33,0:23:30.20,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,無論風有多麼強\N{\c&HFFBF00&}どんなに強い風にも
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:30.27,0:23:35.94,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,也永遠不會折斷的柔婉翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}けして折れない しなやかな羽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.01,0:23:48.55,Lyrics,,0000,0000,0000,,相信有一天  我會擁有那樣一對翅膀\N{\c&HFFBF00&}いつか　きっと持つから
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:51.96,0:23:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（下回預告）\N這件維修服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:53.56,0:23:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是我一針一線細心縫好的哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.60,0:23:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:59.23,0:24:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳好厲害唷，拉薇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縫這個地方的時候很費工夫呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:03.10,0:24:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，我不是要說這個啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:04.64,0:24:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士，你的衣服上\N怎麼會有蘇菲亞的味道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.91,0:24:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:11.54,0:24:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一回，最後流亡 第17話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:14.41,0:24:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,備齊材料\NMaking material
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.98,0:24:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還有迪奧和蓋爾的味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:18.22,0:24:20.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,克勞士
